Name: Air Wars
About the game: The helicopter's journey to its base lies through a crowd of enemies, obstacles and extraterrestrial interventions. Help the helicopter pilot to overcome a difficult route that runs through beautiful landscapes and along the way collecting balloons released into the air that will help to find way home. Features of the game: - Increasing difficulty - Nice visual style - Dynamic music
